item.title: CVE-2022-1538|2024-08-03T00:10:03.024Z -- unknown -- theme%20demo%20import
item.description: Theme Demo Import WordPress plugin before 1.1.1 does not validate the imported file, allowing high-privilege users such as admin to upload arbitrary files (such as PHP) even when FILE_MODS and FILE_EDIT are disallowed.
